definitions.definition: Any of the eighteen isomeric aliphatic hydrocarbons (C 8 H 18 ) found in petroleum , especially an iso-octane 2,2,4 trimethyl-pentane; they are used as fuels and solvents .

main_definition: ( organic chemistry ) Any of the eighteen isomeric aliphatic hydrocarbons (C 8 H 18 ) found in petroleum , especially an iso-octane 2,2,4 trimethyl-pentane; they are used as fuels and solvents .
